---
title: Warm Shrimp, Kale & Apple Chopped Salad with Roasted Sweet Potato, Sunflower Seeds & Lemony Dressing
description: This bright and hearty salad is chock full of nutritious veggies, nutty sunflower seeds, and tender garlicky chicken. Crisp apples and roasted sweet potatoes join the kale and broccoli mix that’s tossed in a fresh lemon-Dijon dressing. Each bite is full of flavor and texture, needing only a final squeeze of lemon to bring it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/667ac78ce4ccb870eb4daf04-85807628.jpeg
